Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Kabbalist26\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Kabbalist26\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 30", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}セフィロトの樹の模様の陣を設置して周期的に味方のHPを回復させます。
Effect: 持続時間#{CaptionTime}#秒{nl}0.5秒ごとに最大HPの#{CaptionRatio}#%回復{nl}聖水10個消費
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Kabbalist25\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Kabbalist25\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = skill.Level", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}自分の基本攻撃に聖属性を付与します。一定時間基本攻撃をすると、聖属性の追加打撃が適用され、体力が40%以下になると効果がさらにアップします。
Effect: 聖属性追加攻撃 +#{CaptionRatio}#{nl}持続時間#{CaptionTime}#秒{nl}ギスロティス1個消費
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Chaplain13\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Chaplain13\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var pcLevel = pc.Lv", "var pcMNA = pc.MNA", "var pcLevelRate = (pcLevel / 6.5) + 15", "var baseDamageValue = 200 + (skill.Level - 1) * pcLevelRate", "var pcMnaRate = (pcMNA / (pcMNA + pcLevel) * 2) + 0.15", "var value = baseDamageValue * pcMnaRate", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Slash] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}巨大なハサミを召喚し、前方の敵を連続で攻撃します。スキル使用中は敵に攻撃を受けてもキャンセルされず、悪魔型の敵に与えるダメージがアップします。
Effect: スキル係数#{SkillFactor}#%{nl}対象数#{CaptionRatio}#{nl}拷問道具2個必要
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["var value = 5", "var STR = pc.STR", "var strValue = STR / 50", "", "if (strValue <= 0) {", "    strValue = 0", "}", "", "value = value + strValue", "return Math.floor(value)"]
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Inquisitor16\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Inquisitor16\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic]{/}{/}{nl}おみくじを引いてその結果によってバフを付与します。大吉、中吉、小吉、小凶、大凶が出ます。それぞれの確率は次の通りです。{nl}* 大吉 : 5%{nl}* 中吉 : 20%{nl}* 小吉 : 50%{nl}* 小凶 : 20%{nl}* 大凶 : 5%
Effect: 持続時間#{CaptionTime}#秒{nl}大吉 : クリティカル発生#{CaptionRatio}#%アップ{nl}中吉 : クリティカル発生#{CaptionRatio2}#%アップ{nl}小吉 : クリティカル発生#{CaptionRatio3}#%アップ{nl}小凶 : 何も起きない{nl}大凶 : クリティカル抵抗50%ダウン{nl}
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Miko7\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Miko7\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 20 * skill.Level", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Name: おみくじ
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}周辺の敵に攻撃を受けると聖属性ダメージを与えるデバフを付与します。
Effect: スキル係数#{SkillFactor}#%{nl}持続時間 #{CaptionRatio}#秒{nl}攻撃可能回数10回{nl}適用対象数10
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Zealot11\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Zealot11\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}幻草薬を飲み、一時的に身体能力を上げ基本攻撃速度がアップします。副作用として持続的にHPがダウンする状態になります。
Effect: 基本攻撃速度#{CaptionRatio}#アップ{nl}#{CaptionRatio2}#秒ごとにHP 1%ずつダウン{nl}持続時間300秒{nl}幻草薬1個消費
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Assassin1\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Assassin1\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 30 + skill.Level * 15", "value = Math.floor(value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill))", "return value;"]

SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"Bunshin_Debuff\") == \"YES\") {", "    var Bunshin = GetSkill(pc, 'Shinobi_Bunshin_no_jutsu')", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + (Bunshin.Level * 2000 + (basicCoolDown * (Bunshin.Level * 0.1)))", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Missile] - [Gun] - [Fire]{/}{/}{nl}爆発させ前方の敵に炎属性ダメージを与えます。{nl}{#00113F}催涙範囲中の敵にナパームバレット使用すると、催涙効果は消え爆発ダメージのみを与えます。{/}

Effect: 基本攻撃の攻撃力#{SkillFactor}#%{nl}基本攻撃が変更される{nl}5レベルマスター
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var sklFactor;", "", "if (skillOwner.ClassName == 'PC') {", "    var atkType = skill.AttackType;", "    var attribute = skill.Attribute;", "    var atkTypebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, atkType);", "    var attributebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, attribute);", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel + atkTypebyItem + attributebyItem;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "} else {", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "}", ""]
